data.description: Lovingly maintained 3 bedroom & 1.75 bath home on a just shy ½ acre lot! Open living area with wood burning FP! Step up into the formal dining area off the kitchen. Galley kitchen provides plenty of cabinet space, prep space, and appliances that stay! Family room with laminate flooring and French doors to the back patio. Primary suite with dual closets & an updated .75 bath ft laminate floors! 2 additional guest rooms and full bathroom. Laundry room with tons of storage! Private, fenced yard with garden space, dog run, outbuildings, patio for entertaining, and spa/hot tub! Huge driveway with room for RV Parking! ~25 minutes to JBLM/McChord. Centrally located near shopping, restaurants, schools, and entertainment!
